From Ian Derby Subject Phils winning the hard way The Phillies have won two games back to back in extra Last night's game was hard The game in Chicago should have been a blow All in all these two games show a different Phillies In past seasons they tended to always be on the short end of run I don't know how many times I saw them losing by only If they were able to win most of those they might have been more of a contending They are so far in extra And of course they are